==Geography==
The Hasdeo–Bango project has been considered as life supporting canal for this district. Under this project 3/4 area of the district will be covered for irrigation. The district headquarters of Janjgir–Champa is Janjgir, which is situated on National Highway 49. Janjgir is 43&nbsp;km from Bilaspur and 152&nbsp;km from State capital [[Raipur]] through the rail route.

